 integrated battery) makes it easy to get on or off the trike, and the cushy seat and upright position add to rider comfort.</p><section id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-19-wrapper" data-type="breaker-ad" class="breaker-ad"><div class="gpt-breaker-container breaker-ad clearfix css-1lttmkl e152u5os0"><div class="css-1cy8om4 e1v257yr0">Advertisement - Continue Reading Below</div><div id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-19" class="ad-container css-14b96eg e1hka4w80"><div id="gpt_lb_19" class="gpt-adslot noskim" style="display: none;"><div id="google_ads_iframe_/36117602/hdm-bicycling/bikes-gear/breaker_20__container__" style="border: 0pt none; margin: auto; text-align: center; width: 728px; height: 0px;"></div></div></div></div></section><p data-node-id="144" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">Use the code <em>CHARGEDUP15</em> at checkout to save 15%!</p><hr data-node-id="145" class="css-18pb4rg et3p2gv0"><h2 data-node-id="146" class="body-h2 css-f5aiel et3p2gv0">BEST TECH</h2><h2 data-node-id="147" class="body-h3 css-jtjq1o et3p2gv0">GoCycle G4 </h2><div data-ad-exclude="(min-width: 90rem)" data-embed="embed-product" data-node-id="148" size="large" class="size-large align-center embed css-aawad4 etrqhn80"><div id="product-92d1bf3c-0321-4306-bbfd-7c7e633dee2b" class="css-17pp2fn etrqhn81"></div><div size="large" class="size-large align-center css-60ezry eyaokey4"><div class="top css-1f1nsoy eyaokey2"><div class="css-1eib4yb e7izsw30">BEST HIGH TECH</div><h2 class="css-v0uqfv e8seki10">Gocycle G4</h2></div><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fgocycle.com%2Fus%2Fwebstore%2Fgocycles%2Fgocycle-g4%2F&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bicycling.com%2Fbikes-gear%2Fa22132137%2Fbest-electric-bikes%2F&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=%5Butm_source%7C%5Butm_campaign%7C%5Butm_medium%7C%5Bgclid%7C%5Bmsclkid%7C%5Bfbclid%7C%5Brefdomain%7Cwww.bicycling.com%5Bcontent_id%7Cd3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e%5Bcontent_product_id%7C