O</em>.</p><section id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-7-wrapper" data-type="breaker-ad" class="breaker-ad"><div class="gpt-breaker-container breaker-ad clearfix css-1lttmkl e152u5os0"><div class="css-1cy8om4 e1v257yr0">Advertisement - Continue Reading Below</div><div id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-7" class="ad-container css-14b96eg e1hka4w80"><div id="gpt_lb_7" class="gpt-adslot noskim" style="display: none;"><div id="google_ads_iframe_/36117602/hdm-bicycling/bikes-gear/breaker_8__container__" style="border: 0pt none; margin: auto; text-align: center; width: 728px; height: 0px;"></div></div></div></div></section><p data-node-id="55" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0"><em><a href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.velotricbike.com%2Fproducts%2Fvelotric-discover-1%3Fvariant%3D41298824495287&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bicycling.com%2Fbikes-gear%2Fa22132137%2Fbest-electric-bikes%2F&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=%5Butm_source%7C%5Butm_campaign%7C%5Butm_medium%7C%5Bgclid%7C%5Bmsclkid%7C%5Bfbclid%7C%5Brefdomain%7Cwww.bicycling.com%5Bcontent_id%7Cd3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e%5Bcontent_product_id%7Ce085b196-4870-46a1-812f-7eb275768ea5%5Bproduct_retailer_id%7Ca81e36f6-85ae-4fea-af6e-b6cb8c6ec587%5Blt%7Csale" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.velotricbike.com/products/velotric-discover-1?variant=41298824495287" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="AVAILABLE IN STEP-THROUGH" rel="nofollow" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-href="https://www.velotricbike.com/products/velotric-discover-1?variant=41298824495287" data-vars-ga-product-id="e085b196-4870-46a1-812f-7eb275768ea5" data-affiliate="true" data-affiliate-url="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.velotricbike.com%2Fproducts%2Fvelotric-discover-1%3Fvariant%3D41298824495287" data-affiliate-network="{}" data-vars-ga-media-role="" data-vars-ga-media-type="" data-vars-ga-product-brand="" data-vars-ga-product-price="$1,199.00" data-vars-ga-p