ass=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>High payload and hauling capacity</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Powerful motor</li></ul></div><div class="css-aqsj2r ektooqb6"><h6 class="css-ytm8f ektooqb5">Cons</h6><ul class="css-1r2eg5o ektooqb4"><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb2"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/x-circle.32fa08e.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Con" role="img" title="Con" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb0"></span>Overall weight</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb2"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/x-circle.32fa08e.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Con" role="img" title="Con" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb0"></span>Slightly flexy stem</li></ul></div></div></div><p data-node-id="80" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">Aventon’s Abound is a highly capable and competitively priced mid-tail cargo-hauling e-bike. And it has the features, power, and options to carry needed for carrying almost anything by bike. The Abound’s 750-watt read hub motor with torque controller provides a zippy ride feel, Tektro hydraulic brakes with 180mm rotors provide strong stopping power, and other features like the dropper post help the bike outperform similarly priced competition.  The bike’s internal battery provides up to a 50-mile range (though we experienced about 25 miles using the highest power setting and the throttle). The Abound’s reinforced rack accommodates passengers up to 143 lb., with a total bike capacity of 440 lb. </p><p data-node-id="81" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0"><em><a href="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/a43100171/aventon-abound-review/" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/a43100171/aventon-abound-review/" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="READ FULL REVIEW" rel="nofollow" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" class="body-btn-link css-1146q7 et3p2gv0">READ FULL REVIEW</a></em></p><hr data-node-id="82" class="css-18pb4rg et3p2gv0"><h2 data-node-id="83" class="body-h2 css-f5aiel et3p2gv0">BEST FAT TIRE COMMUTER</h2><h2 data-node-id="84" class="body-h3 css-jtjq1o et3p2gv0">Rad Power RadRover 6 Plus</h2><div data-ad-exclude="(min-width: 90rem)" data-embed="embed-product" data-node-id="85" size="large" class="size-large align-center embed css-aawad4 etrqhn80"><div id="product-cd3a03fa-12ce-4c7f-bd38-aaacebdba385" class="css-17pp2fn etrqhn81"></div><div size="large" class="size-large align-center css-60ezry eyaokey4"><div class="top css-1f1nsoy eyaokey2"><div class="css-1eib4yb e7izsw30">BEST FAT TIRE COMMUTER</div><h2 class="css-v0uqfv e8seki10">Rad Power Bikes RadRover 6 Plus</h2></div><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.radpowerbikes.com%2Fproducts%2Fradrover-plus-electric-fat-tire-bike&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bicycling.com%2Fbikes-gear%2Fa22132137%2Fbest-electric-bikes%2F&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=%5Butm_source%7C%5Butm_campaign%7C%5Butm_medium%7C%5Bgclid%7C%5Bmsclkid%7C%5Bfbclid%7C%5Brefdomain%7Cwww.bicycling.com%5Bcontent_id%7Cd3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e%5Bcontent_product_id%7Ccd3a03fa-12ce-4c7f-bd38-aaacebdba385%5Bproduct_retailer_id%7Cb011abd3-f054-4c0f-8406-774284fee8c0%5Blt%7C" data-href="https://www.radpowerbikes.com/products/radrover-plus-electric-fat-tire-bik