ata-vars-ga-call-to-action="$1,200 at Aventon Bikes" data-vars-ga-media-type="Single Product Embed" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.aventon.com/products/pace-350-ebike" data-vars-ga-product-brand="Aventon" data-vars-ga-product-id="6d4cba44-7ee6-4f82-b0af-26b6856d087e" data-vars-ga-product-price="$1,200.00" data-vars-ga-product-retailer-id="c437b15c-afd2-43f0-bbae-095659fabc43" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-category="Languages &amp; Tools" data-vars-ga-gallery-id="" data-vars-ga-link-treatment="sale | (not set)" data-vars-ga-sku="aventon_pace-350-ebike" data-vars-ga-magento-tracking="1" role="button" data-ab-label="ProdClick" class="product-btn-link en6kra60 css-17x8gcl epl65fo4" data-skimlinks-tracking="[utm_source|[utm_campaign|[utm_medium|[gclid|[msclkid|[fbclid|[refdomain|www.bicycling.com[content_id|d3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e[content_product_id|6d4cba44-7ee6-4f82-b0af-26b6856d087e[product_retailer_id|c437b15c-afd2-43f0-bbae-095659fabc43[lt|sale">$1,200 at Aventon Bikes</a></div></div></div><div class="css-tnkfjl ektooqb7"><div class="css-aqsj2r ektooqb6"><h6 class="css-ytm8f ektooqb5">Pros</h6><ul class="css-1r2eg5o ektooqb4"><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Great bike at a great price</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Updated frame with integrated battery</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span> Integrated brake light</li></ul></div><div class="css-aqsj2r ektooqb6"><h6 class="css-ytm8f ektooqb5">Cons</h6><ul class="css-1r2eg5o ektooqb4"><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb2"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/x-circle.32fa08e.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Con" role="img" title="Con" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb0"></span>Only black or grey color options</li></ul></div></div><div class="css-0 e1kz309q1"><table class="css-165pmwm ekv9bgd3"><tbody><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">POWER</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">350W</td></tr><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">WEIGHT</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">49 lb.</td></tr><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">TOP SPEED</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">20 mph</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p data-node-id="134" class="body-text css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">Aventon recently updated its already outstanding Pace range with a brand new frame and fork, integrated battery, and tail lights sleekly designed into the seat stays. At $1,300, the Aventon Pace 350 continues to deliver an outstanding balance of price and performance, now with a fresh new look. As a Class 2 e-bike, it has a max pedal-assist speed of 20 mph along with a thumb-controlled throttle. The Pace 350 rolls on 27.5 x 2.2-inch e-bike-rated tires and stops via mechanical disc brakes. A 7-speed Shimano drivetrain and five levels of pedal assist provide you with various options. The bike doesn’t have fenders or integrated racks, but the Pace 350 felt viable for daily commuting. </p><section id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-18-wrapper" data-type="breaker-ad" class="breaker-ad"><div cl