</div></div><div></div></div></div><div class="vjs-wrapper"></div></div></div></div><p data-node-id="159" class="body-tip css-11ym6pp et3p2gv0"><a href="https://www.bicycling.com/email/bicycling-newsletter" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.bicycling.com/email/bicycling-newsletter" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="📧  To always be in the know, sign up for our newsletter" rel="nofollow" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" class="body-btn-link css-1146q7 et3p2gv0">📧  To always be in the know, sign up for our newsletter</a></p><div class="css-2ok9l4 e13rjwo40"><div class="css-1me4wps e19xk9rq7"><span class="css-irehmq e19xk9rq1"><img width="540" height="540" alt="Headshot of Tara Seplavy" title="This is an image" fetchpriority="auto" decoding="async" src="https://hips.hearstapps.com/rover/profile_photos/17816e75-c3b6-4b6e-a4b0-9066a1823338_1644009404.file" size="auto" srcset="https://hips.hearstapps.com/rover/profile_photos/17816e75-c3b6-4b6e-a4b0-9066a1823338_1644009404.file" loading="lazy" class="lqip lazyloaded css-o0wq4v e1lki9i00 ls-is-cached"></span><div><div class="css-3sqxrq e19xk9rq6"><span class="css-0 e19xk9rq4"><a href="/author/238358/tara-seplavy/" class="epl65fo3 css-njmgv8 epl65fo4"><span>Tara Seplavy</span></a></span></div><div class="css-1pq7n1y e19xk9rq5">Deputy Editor</div><div class="css-11ash57 e19xk9rq3"><p>As Deputy Editor, Tara Seplavy leads Bicycling’s product test team; after having previously led product development and sourcing for multiple bike brands, run World Championship winning mountain bike teams, wrenched at renowned bicycle shops in Brooklyn, raced everything from criteriums to downhill, and ridden bikes on six different continents (landing herself in hospital emergency rooms in four countries and counting). Based in Easton, Pennsylvania, Tara spends tons of time on the road and trail testing products. A familiar face at cyclocross races, crits, and bike parks in the Mid Atlantic and New England, on weekends she can often be found racing for the New York City-based CRCA/KruisCX team. When not riding a bike, or talking about them, Tara listens to a lot of ska, punk, and emo music, and consumes too much social media. &nbsp;</p></div><a href="/author/238358/tara-seplavy/" class="epl65fo3 css-2m8fjc epl65fo4">Read full bio</a></div></div></div><div id="journey-inline" class="css-ciejky e1cslvxz0"></div></div>', 'DRAFT', 'https://example.com/thumbnail3.jpg', 'https://example.com/cover_image3.jpg', 1, '2023-03-10 12:00:00.000000', 1, '2023-03-10 12:00:00.000000', 1, false, 19, 'Add more zip to every trip with e-bikes for every type of rider.'),
        (39, 'The Best Gravel Bikes You Can Buy Right Now', '<div class="article-body-content article-body longform-body css-z6i669 ewisyje7"><p data-node-id="0" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">No segment of bicycles is growing faster than electric bikes—and that demand is good for you, the e-bike shopper. Newer brands like <a href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2F&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bicycling.com%2Fbikes-gear%2Fa22132137%2Fbest-electric-bikes%2F&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=%5Butm_source%7C%5Butm_campaign%7C%5Butm_medium%7C%5Bgclid%7C%5Bmsclkid%7C%5Bfbclid%7C%5Brefdomain%7Cwww.bicycling.com%5Bcontent_id%7Cd3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e%5Bcontent_product_id%7C27cd79d5-783b-455c-9e9c-189bbc07f9b9%5Bproduct_retailer_id%7C25620da0-495e-4f98-926a-5c4959f40bc0%5Blt%7C" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.aventon.com/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="Aventon" data-href="https://www.aventon.com/" data-vars-ga-product-id="27cd79d5-783b-455c-9e9c-189bbc07f9b9" data-affiliate="true" data-affiliate-url="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2F" data-affiliate-network="{}" data-vars-ga-media-role="" data-vars-ga-media-type="" data-vars-ga-product-brand="aventon.com" data-vars-ga-product-price="" data-vars-ga-product-retailer-id="25620da0-495e-4f98-926a-5c4959f40bc0" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-brand="aventon.com" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-category="Europe" data-vars-ga-gallery-id="" data-vars-ga-link-treatment="(not set) | (not set)" class="body-link product-links css-qlm9kn et3p2gv0" data-skimlinks-tracking="[utm_source|[utm_campaign|[utm_medium|[gclid|[msclkid|[fbclid|[refdomain|www.bicycling.com[content_id|d3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e[content_product_id|27cd79d5-783b-455c-9e9c-189bbc07f9b9[product_retailer_id|25620da0-495e-4f98-926a-5c4959f40bc0[lt|">Aventon</a>, <a href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X15762