ll-to-action="Trek" class="body-link css-qlm9kn et3p2gv0">Trek</a>, and <a href="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/mountain-bike/a41023476/pivot-shuttle-lt/" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/mountain-bike/a41023476/pivot-shuttle-lt/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="Pivot" class="body-link css-qlm9kn et3p2gv0">Pivot</a>.</p><div size="medium" data-embed="body-image" data-node-id="1" class="align-center size-medium embed css-1736von e1xqj1sx4"><div class="css-uwraif e1xqj1sx3"><img alt="specialized turbo vado 40" title="Specialized Turbo Vado 4.0" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/specialized-tubo-vado-0006-preview-maxwidth-3000-maxheight-3000-ppi-300-quality-90-1632231904.jpg?crop=0.997xw:0.949xh;0.00340xw,0&amp;resize=640:* 640w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/specialized-tubo-vado-0006-preview-maxwidth-3000-maxheight-3000-ppi-300-quality-90-1632231904.jpg?crop=0.997xw:0.949xh;0.00340xw,0&amp;resize=768:* 980w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/specialized-tubo-vado-0006-preview-maxwidth-3000-maxheight-3000-ppi-300-quality-90-1632231904.jpg?crop=0.997xw:0.949xh;0.00340xw,0&amp;resize=980:* 1120w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/specialized-tubo-vado-0006-preview-maxwidth-3000-maxheight-3000-ppi-300-quality-90-1632231904.jpg?crop=0.997xw:0.949xh;0.00340xw,0&amp;resize=980:* 1200w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/specialized-tubo-vado-0006-preview-maxwidth-3000-maxheight-3000-ppi-300-quality-90-1632231904.jpg?crop=0.997xw:0.949xh;0.00340xw,0&amp;resize=980:* 1920w" src="https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/specialized-tubo-vado-0006-preview-maxwidth-3000-maxheight-3000-ppi-300-quality-90-1632231904.jpg?crop=0.997xw:0.949xh;0.00340xw,0&amp;resize=980:*" width="3000" height="2000" decoding="async" data-nimg="future" loading="lazy" style="color: transparent; width: 100%; height: auto;" class="css-0 exi4f7p0"><div class="css-swqnqv e1xqj1sx2"><figcaption class="css-1am3yn9 enfs9c50"><span class="css-zwwov0 e6iqukd2">Trevor Raab</span></figcaption></div></div></div><p data-node-id="2" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">Designs keep improving, tech is becoming more reliable, and capabilities are expanding. Whether you purchase online or through a retailer, you can find everything from <a href="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/a25102796/best-folding-e-bikes/" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/a25102796/best-folding-e-bikes/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="folding e-bikes" class="body-link css-qlm9kn et3p2gv0">folding e-bikes</a>, <a href="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/a33313406/best-fat-tire-ebikes/" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/a33313406/best-fat-tire-ebikes/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="fat-tire e-bikes" class="body-link css-qlm9kn et3p2gv0">fat-tire e-bikes</a>, electric-assist road bikes, and a sea of commuter and city electric bikes. Liberated from some of the standard bike constraints like weight and gearing, e-bike design has exploded.</p><div size="medium" data-embed="body-image" data-node-id="3" class="align-center size-medium embed css-1736von e1xqj1sx4"><div class="css-uwraif e1xqj1sx3"><img alt="rad power radmission electric hybrid bike ridden by amy wolff in easton, pa in october 2022" title="rad power RadMission Electric Hybrid Bike ridden by Amy Wolff in Easton, PA in October 2022" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/rad-power-commuter-story-amy-trevor-0043-1665421064.jpeg?resize=640:* 640w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/rad-power-commuter-story-amy-trevor-0043-1665421064.jpeg?resize=768:* 980w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/rad-power-commuter-story-amy-trevor-0043-1665421064.jpeg?resize=980:* 1120w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/rad-power-commuter-story-amy-trevor-0043-1665421064.jpeg?resize=980:* 1200w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/rad-power-commuter-story-amy-trevor-0043-1665421064.jpeg?resize=980:* 1920w" src="https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/rad-power-commuter-story-amy-trevor-0043-1665421064.jpeg?resize=980:*" width="2000" height="1333" decoding="async" data-nimg="future" loading="lazy" style="color: transparent; width: 100%; height: auto;" class="css-0 exi4f7p0"><div class="css-swqnqv e1xqj1sx2"><figcaption class="css-1am3yn9 enfs9c50"><span class="css-zwwov0 e6iqukd2">Trevor Raab</span></figcaption></div></div></div><section id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-top-wrapper" data-type="breaker-ad" class="breaker-ad"><div class="gpt-breaker-container breaker-ad clearfix css-1lttmkl e152u5os0"><div class="css-1cy8om4 e1v257yr0">Advertisement - Continue Reading Below</div><div id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-top" class="ad-container css-14b96eg e1hka4w80"><div id="gpt_lb_top" class="gpt-adslot noskim" style="display: none;"><div id="google_ads_iframe_/36117602/hdm-bicycling/bikes-gear/breaker_0__container__" style="border: 0pt none; margin: auto; text-align: center; width: 728px; height: 0px;"></div></div></div></div></section><p data-node-id="4" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">To make these reviews as helpful as possible, we focused on lower to mid-price options from brands you can purchase directly online—though we did include a couple of recommendations for more expensive e-bikes that our team of bike testers loved.</p><p data-node-id="5" class="body-tip css-11ym6pp et3p2gv0">If you are looking for a higher-performance e-bike—or specifically want the help and service you can get from a specialty retailer—be sure to check out recommendations for our <a href="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/a36949725/ebike-awards-2021/" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.bicycling.com/bikes-gear/a36949725/ebike-awards-2021/" data-vars-