treatment="(not set) | (not set)" data-vars-ga-sku="206161" data-vars-ga-magento-tracking="1" role="button" data-ab-label="ProdClick" class="product-btn-link en6kra60 css-17x8gcl epl65fo4" data-skimlinks-tracking="[utm_source|[utm_campaign|[utm_medium|[gclid|[msclkid|[fbclid|[refdomain|www.bicycling.com[content_id|d3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e[content_product_id|834effae-c500-450a-a4b6-1e8e29e144e6[product_retailer_id|bc03a965-168e-41ee-9896-69c673dd625c[lt|">$4,000 at Specialized</a></div></div></div><div class="css-tnkfjl ektooqb7"><div class="css-aqsj2r ektooqb6"><h6 class="css-ytm8f ektooqb5">Pros</h6><ul class="css-1r2eg5o ektooqb4"><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Extremely functional and well thought-out.</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Motor has a powerful, smooth, and natural feeling.</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Lots of colors and size options.</li></ul></div><div class="css-aqsj2r ektooqb6"><h6 class="css-ytm8f ektooqb5">Cons</h6><ul class="css-1r2eg5o ektooqb4"><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb2"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/x-circle.32fa08e.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Con" role="img" title="Con" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb0"></span>Pricier than competitors.</li></ul></div></div><div class="css-0 e1kz309q1"><table class="css-165pmwm ekv9bgd3"><tbody><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">POWER</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">70Nm</td></tr><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">WEIGHT</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">57.5 lb.</td></tr><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">TOP SPEED</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">28 mph</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p data-node-id="99" class="body-text css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0"><br></p><p data-node-id="100" class="body-text css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">Specialized''s Turbo Vado 4.0 just feels ''<em>right</em>''. From the motor to the interface to the aesthetic design to the parts selection to the ride quality, the details on the Turbo Vado 4.0 have all been thoroughly thought through to perform as a seamless package. This is a rare quality that anyone—be they a lifelong cyclist or getting their first e-bike—can benefit from and enjoy.<br></p><p data-node-id="101" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">We have ridden a lot of e-bikes over the years, and the Specialized Turbo models consistently test amongst the best in all categories. The brand puts a ton of development time into its Turbo series e-bikes by refining the motor tune and carefully selecting parts. This work pays off with best-in-class ride quality. If you have been hesitant to try an e-bike because you think it won''t feel like your favorite non-assist bike, try a Specialized Turbo. You''ll quickly become a convert.</p><section id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-13-wrapper" data-type="breaker-ad" class="breaker-ad"><div class="gpt-breaker-container breaker-ad clearfix css-1lttmkl e152u5os0"><div class="css-1cy8om4 e1v257yr0">Advertisement - Continue Reading Below</div><div id="article