a-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Excellent performance and value</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>New torque sensor, lights, and LCD head unit</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Rack, fenders, and hydraulic disc brakes</li></ul></div><div class="css-aqsj2r ektooqb6"><h6 class="css-ytm8f ektooqb5">Cons</h6><ul class="css-1r2eg5o ektooqb4"></ul></div></div><div class="css-0 e1kz309q1"><table class="css-165pmwm ekv9bgd3"><tbody><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">Power</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">500W</td></tr><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">Weight</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">59.8 lb.</td></tr><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">Top Speed</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">28 mph</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p data-node-id="39" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">Aventon updated its outstanding Level e-bike to have a smoother ride and added visibility. A new torque sensor delivers power to the rear hub motor more evenly than the previous generation bike. The Level.2 has a more natural and intuitive feel when riding. The integrated lights and a smaller, easier-to-use display help make one of our favorite commuter e-bikes even better.</p><section id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-5-wrapper" data-type="breaker-ad" class="breaker-ad"><div class="gpt-breaker-container breaker-ad clearfix css-1lttmkl e152u5os0"><div class="css-1cy8om4 e1v257yr0">Advertisement - Continue Reading Below</div><div id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-5" class="ad-container css-14b96eg e1hka4w80"><div id="gpt_lb_5" class="gpt-adslot noskim" style="display: none;"><div id="google_ads_iframe_/36117602/hdm-bicycling/bikes-gear/breaker_6__container__" style="border: 0pt none; margin: auto; text-align: center; width: 728px; height: 0px;"></div></div></div></div></section><p data-node-id="40" class="css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">In our testing, the Level.2 performed better than expected in every situation. The Aventon Level.2 remains the best commuter e-bike you can purchase for less than $2,000 and one of the best commuter bikes you can buy overall. The updates to the platform make an already great bike even better. Aventon still has the <a href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Flevel-ebike-v1&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bicycling.com%2Fbikes-gear%2Fa22132137%2Fbest-electric-bikes%2F&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=%5Butm_source%7C%5Butm_campaign%7C%5Butm_medium%7C%5Bgclid%7C%5Bmsclkid%7C%5Bfbclid%7C%5Brefdomain%7Cwww.bicycling.com%5Bcontent_id%7Cd3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e%5Bcontent_product_id%7Cb5ea5d8d-50f4-4d59-bb15-c5bfa7fee2f7%5Bproduct_retailer_id%7C3dc09f34-a8ba-40f6-a5fb-f827f8882720%5Blt%7C" target="_blank" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.aventon.com/products/level-ebike-v1" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="first-generation Level" data-href="https://www.aventon.com/products/level-ebike-v1" data-vars-ga-product-id="b5ea5d8d-50f4-4d59-bb15-c5bfa7fee2f7" data-affiliate="true" data-affiliate-url="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Flevel-ebike-v1" data-affiliate-network="{}" d