act Neo 20</h2></div><div size="large" class="size-large css-12bdcfv e1a1omje0"><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fmikesbikes.com%2Fproducts%2Fcompact-neo-20&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bicycling.com%2Fbikes-gear%2Fa22132137%2Fbest-electric-bikes%2F&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=%5Butm_source%7C%5Butm_campaign%7C%5Butm_medium%7C%5Bgclid%7C%5Bmsclkid%7C%5Bfbclid%7C%5Brefdomain%7Cwww.bicycling.com%5Bcontent_id%7Cd3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e%5Bcontent_product_id%7Cef587ede-080b-4393-a548-fbe331b5247a%5Bproduct_retailer_id%7Cac0257a0-2e7b-4270-9f1d-848865a8049c%5Blt%7C" data-href="https://mikesbikes.com/products/compact-neo-20" aria-label="$1,825 at mikesbikes.com for Compact Neo 20" data-affiliate="true" data-affiliate-url="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1576257&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fmikesbikes.com%2Fproducts%2Fcompact-neo-20" data-affiliate-network="{}" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="$1,825 at mikesbikes.com" data-vars-ga-media-type="Single Product Embed" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://mikesbikes.com/products/compact-neo-20" data-vars-ga-product-brand="Cannondale" data-vars-ga-product-id="ef587ede-080b-4393-a548-fbe331b5247a" data-vars-ga-product-price="$1,824.99" data-vars-ga-product-retailer-id="ac0257a0-2e7b-4270-9f1d-848865a8049c" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-category="Electronica" data-vars-ga-gallery-id="" data-vars-ga-link-treatment="(not set) | (not set)" data-vars-ga-sku="compact-neo-20" data-vars-ga-magento-tracking="1" role="button" data-ab-label="ProdClick" class="product-btn-link en6kra60 css-17x8gcl epl65fo4" data-skimlinks-tracking="[utm_source|[utm_campaign|[utm_medium|[gclid|[msclkid|[fbclid|[refdomain|www.bicycling.com[content_id|d3e2a1e6-a1f1-4b66-94af-a513e9ba1f4e[content_product_id|ef587ede-080b-4393-a548-fbe331b5247a[product_retailer_id|ac0257a0-2e7b-4270-9f1d-848865a8049c[lt|">$1,825 at mikesbikes.com</a></div></div></div><div class="css-tnkfjl ektooqb7"><div class="css-aqsj2r ektooqb6"><h6 class="css-ytm8f ektooqb5">Pros</h6><ul class="css-1r2eg5o ektooqb4"><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Practical folding features</li><li class="css-9ee16j ektooqb3"><span aria-hidden="true" class=" css-4bs81v e1s64tyo0"><img data-dynamic-svg="" src="/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/plus-circle.f37c4a9.svg?primary=%2523067EA7" loading="lazy" alt="Pro" role="img" title="Pro" height="auto" width="auto" class="css-23kqqm ektooqb1"></span>Light and portable</li></ul></div><div class="css-aqsj2r ektooqb6"><h6 class="css-ytm8f ektooqb5">Cons</h6><ul class="css-1r2eg5o ektooqb4"></ul></div></div><div class="css-0 e1kz309q1"><table class="css-165pmwm ekv9bgd3"><tbody><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">POWER</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">250W</td></tr><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">WEIGHT</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">39.8 lb.</td></tr><tr class="css-0 ekv9bgd2"><th class="css-1xje7yg ekv9bgd0">TOP SPEED</th><td class="css-13w75t5 ekv9bgd1">20 mph</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p data-node-id="94" class="body-text css-18vfmjb et3p2gv0">Don''t let the Neo''s 20-inch tires fool you—this compact wheel e-bike rides better than many full-sized bikes. With a visual profile reminiscent of 1990s Cannondale''s Killer V mountain bikes, the Compact Neo cleverly hides a 250Wh battery in the bike''s downtube to make it almost indistinguishable from traditional acoustic bikes. The Compact Neo is light enough to carry upstairs or onto the train. And, the bike''s foldable stem makes the bike more practical than some full folding bikes.</p><section id="article-ad-breaker-leaderboard-12-wrapper" data-type="b